{"id":767,"date":"2023-04-21T14:51:09","date_gmt":"2023-04-21T14:51:09","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/wgl-dsites.net\/bladehub\/?p=767"},"modified":"2023-04-24T12:11:52","modified_gmt":"2023-04-24T12:11:52","slug":"modern-barbers-collection-of-the-month","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/wgl-dsites.net\/bladehub\/modern-barbers-collection-of-the-month\/","title":{"rendered":"Modern Barber\u2019s Collection of the Month"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-post\" data-elementor-id=\"767\" class=\"elementor elementor-767\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-914fdcf elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"914fdcf\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-f897673\" data-id=\"f897673\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cf47afe elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"cf47afe\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span class=\"dropcap primary\">R<\/span>unning your own business in the hair and beauty industry can be tough, with everything from finances to marketing, and team management to consider. Here, Booksy Ambassador, Ruger Barber Director and world-renowned Barber, Alan Beak shares his top tips to get your business ready for 2023. There are many barbershops and service-providing industries, and we fight constantly with new businesses opening, which is great for whatever industry you\u2019re in as it shows growth in that field,\u201d says Alan. \u201cBut if you want to continue to grow, then you must look at what other people are offering and do more or do better. So, should you find the start of the year a quieter time, you can use this time wisely to vamp up your shop, upskill, and network as much as you can.<\/p><p><em>Preparation for everything this year is paramount. We have decided to sit down as a team and brainstorm any issue we may face \u2013 things like quiet times, no-shows, and late cancellations. Now we have out list of possible difficulties, we will put processes in place like marketing techniques and setting up no-show protection. <\/em><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a0fddc0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"a0fddc0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-e9014c2 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"e9014c2\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-8407552\" data-id=\"8407552\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-baae364 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"baae364\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"840\" height=\"660\" src=\"https:\/\/wgl-dsites.net\/bladehub\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/blog-s-1.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-74\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wgl-dsites.net\/bladehub\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/blog-s-1.jpg 840w, https:\/\/wgl-dsites.net\/bladehub\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/blog-s-1-300x236.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wgl-dsites.net\/bladehub\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/blog-s-1-768x603.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 840px) 100vw, 840px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-8bd6dcc\" data-id=\"8bd6dcc\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-72acf58 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"72acf58\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"840\" height=\"660\" src=\"https:\/\/wgl-dsites.net\/bladehub\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/blog-s-2.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-76\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wgl-dsites.net\/bladehub\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/blog-s-2.jpg 840w, https:\/\/wgl-dsites.net\/bladehub\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/blog-s-2-300x236.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wgl-dsites.net\/bladehub\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/blog-s-2-768x603.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 840px) 100vw, 840px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-12e46d6 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"12e46d6\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-0b4feaf\" data-id=\"0b4feaf\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fdc4f92 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"fdc4f92\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-11709ae aleft elementor-widget elementor-widget-wgl-double-heading\" data-id=\"11709ae\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"wgl-double-heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"wgl-double-heading\"><h3 class=\"dblh__title-wrapper\"><span class=\"dblh__title dblh__title-1\">Prepare for everything<\/span><\/h3><\/div>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6685062 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6685062\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Staying organised is essential for a well-oiled business and making sure <span style=\"color: var(--bladehub-header-font-color); font-weight: 600;\">you keep yourself and everyone happy<\/span>. I like having 30 minutes every morning to create a job list and allocate time to work on these jobs during the day. If I try to do them between clients, I can easily lose track and get lost, so having set times during the day that I block out is better. I always used the acronym FOCUS \u2013 Following One Course Until Successful.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cf90b63 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"cf90b63\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<blockquote>\u201cThe Barbers is an affordable, convenient and good quality to get my hair cut. It is a friendly, laid back environment with great professionals\u201d<cite>TYLER SMITH<\/cite><\/blockquote>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0e6ef2b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"0e6ef2b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tCertain jobs take precedence over others and can change as the day or week goes on, so when I do my job list, I often put a star next to the jobs of higher priority. If a staff member becomes <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: #9B9B9B;\">ill and appointments need changing<\/span> or rescheduling, this automatically becomes high priority as our clients are the most important people and it\u2019s imperative that they are taken care of and not messed around.\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1b15de3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"1b15de3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-8878ac2 elementor-section-content-middle elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"8878ac2\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-2fa5559\" data-id=\"2fa5559\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bb7bc20 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"bb7bc20\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"840\" height=\"660\" src=\"https:\/\/wgl-dsites.net\/bladehub\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/blog-s-3.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-91\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wgl-dsites.net\/bladehub\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/blog-s-3.jpg 840w, https:\/\/wgl-dsites.net\/bladehub\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/blog-s-3-300x236.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wgl-dsites.net\/bladehub\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/blog-s-3-768x603.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 840px) 100vw, 840px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-7eb6054\" data-id=\"7eb6054\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e0a590a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e0a590a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Boosting your business in 2023 is about your services and experience. Having an online presence is great and looks fantastic to your peers. More importantly, it\u2019s important to have a better physical following than a virtual one, and that\u2019s my advice for the year.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1368b6c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1368b6c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"bladehub_dot list_primary_color\"><li>High-quality services and care<\/li><li>Men hair coloring &amp; refreshing hair wash<\/li><li>Relaxing head &amp; shoulders massage<\/li><li>Focus on the people.<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-acaf7c9 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"acaf7c9\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-66c3844\" data-id=\"66c3844\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-81cee4a elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"81cee4a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5cfe7bd elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5cfe7bd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tI tend to plan as I go as things change constantly. Having a planner and detailed calendar is so important for me to be organised. If an external job comes in and I need to book out my time on Booksy, I try to do this as early as possible to make sure I don\u2019t have to reschedule many appointments, but should something short notice arrive, <span style=\"color: var(--bladehub-header-font-color); font-weight: 600;\">I know I can reach my entire client list with the message blast system and get a message to everyone with no hassle.<\/span>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Running your own business in the hair and beauty industry can be tough, with everything from finances to marketing, and team management to consider. Here, Booksy Ambassador, Ruger Barber Director and world-renowned Barber, Alan Beak shares his top tips to get your business ready for 2023. There are many barbershops and service-providing industries, and we [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":652,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[21],"tags":[17,19,18],"class_list":["post-767","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-hairstyles","tag-barber","tag-barbershop","tag-beard"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/wgl-dsites.net\/bladehub\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/767","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/wgl-dsites.net\/bladehub\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/wgl-dsites.net\/bladehub\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wgl-dsites.net\/bladehub\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wgl-dsites.net\/bladehub\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=767"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/wgl-dsites.net\/bladehub\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/767\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wgl-dsites.net\/bladehub\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/652"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/wgl-dsites.net\/bladehub\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=767"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wgl-dsites.net\/bladehub\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=767"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wgl-dsites.net\/bladehub\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=767"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}